The implementable controller is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u\left(t\right)=\Phi\left(Q\left(t\right),\hat{\theta}\left(t\right)\right)+K_{P}e\left(t\right)+K_{D}\dot{e}\left(t\right)+\intop^{t}_{t_{0}}\left(K_{I}e\left(\tau\right)+K_{\text{RISE}}\text{sgn}\left(r_{1}\left(\tau\right)\right)\right)d\tau
\]

\end_inset

where
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
K_{P} & \triangleq k_{1}k_{2}+k_{1}k_{3}+k_{2}k_{3}+1\\
K_{I} & \triangleq k_{1}k_{2}k_{3}+k_{1}\\
K_{D} & \triangleq k_{1}+k_{2}+k_{3}
\end{align*}

